    section
      .block
        .uk-container
          .uk-text-center.uk-position-center#whiteColor
            div
              u
                h1.uk-heading-primary Hi I'm Jonathan.
              h2.uk-margin-left.uk-margin-right Software engineer and a handyman with a green thumb
          div.uk-text-center.uk-position-bottom#whiteColor
            h3.uk-padding-remove-bottom.uk-margin-remove-bottom Check me out
            a(href='#projects', uk-scroll, uk-icon='icon: arrow-down; ratio: 2').uk-margin-bottom
        
    
    section.uk-section.uk-section-muted#projects
      .uk-container
        header.uk-text-center
          h1#secondaryColorText Projects
        h3.uk-text-center.uk-margin-medium-bottom The following are projects that have completed or I am currently working on
      .uk-container.uk-padding-medium
        dl.uk-description-list.uk-description-list-divider
          dt Where's Waldo ( in development )
          dd A computer vision program that will look for Waldo

          dt Shuttle ( On hold )
          dd A web app in which user's can request their ride destination for UCR's shuttle program. The app will determine the most optimal route from all requested routes using A* search alogirhtm.
          
          dt Twitch Analytics ( On hold )
          dd A web app to determine if there is correalation between a Twitch streamer viewership and popular clips of the streamer posted on Reddit. The correlation will be determined using linear regression. A sentiment dictionary will be used to determine if the clip invoked a positive or negative reaction.

          dt Graphing Calculator for Android
          dd A graphing calculator based on Desmos calculator

          dt Synthesizer
          dd A embedded system using an atmega1284, raspberry pi and the Arduino Uno.
            a(href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aegn7HOzvMA')  Video of the Synthesizer.

          dt Dodging Game
          dd A embedded system using an atmega1284 in which the player has to dodge obstacles through various levels
            a(href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TZeS5Vxri7U')  Video of the Dodging Game.

      .uk-container.uk-text-center.uk-padding-large#secondaryColorText
        h3 For more projects checkout my github
        a(href='https://github.com/jherr029', uk-icon='icon: github; ratio: 4')

      hr.uk-divider-icon
        
    
    #aboutMe
    section.uk-section.uk-section-small.uk-background-muted
      .uk-container
        .uk-column-1-2
          .uk-container.uk-margin-top
            .uk-text-center
              .uk-text-lead About Me
            p.
             I graduated from Univerisity of California Riverside with a Bachelor of Science in Computer Science.
             Ever since I was a kid, I was always fascinated by robots in cartoons. I wanted to build one of my own, so I decided
             really early on I wanted to become an engineer. As I got older, I realized I was instead fascinated by the conscious
             of the robot rather than the hardware. That is how I ended in picking up programming. My hobbies include gardening, tinkering
             and making sure my husky is not causing trouble around the house.
            
          img(src='images/icons/robot.svg')

    section.uk-section.uk-background-muted.uk-padding-remove-top.uk-padding-remove-bottom
      .uk-container.uk-padding.uk-text-center
        h2#primaryColor Interest
        .uk-text-center(class='uk-child-width-expand@s', uk-grid='')
          div
            img(src="images/icons/learn.svg", height="150", width='150')
            p.uk-text-bold Machine Learning
          div
            img(src="images/icons/data.svg", height="150", width='150')
            p.uk-text-bold Data Visualization
          div
            img(src="images/icons/vision.svg", height="150", width='150')
            p.uk-text-bold Computer Vision
          div
            img(src="images/icons/stack.svg", height="150", width='150')
            p.uk-text-bold Full Stack Development

        p.uk-text-bold#primaryColor Hire Me !
        p.uk-text-lead I am currently looking for employment
        div
          a.uk-button.uk-button-default.uk-align-center.uk-width-1-3(href='files/ResumeJH.pdf')#secondaryColor Check out my resume

    .container
      block content
        

